  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2019-06-10",
    "date": "2020-02-07T14:29:10Z",
    "text": "Safe Disposal of Opioids Act of 2019\n\nThis bill directs the Department of Justice to award grants to establish or maintain disposal sites for unwanted prescription medications.\n\nAdditionally, the bill imposes a fee on the sale of an active opioid by the manufacturer, producer, or importer. The Department of Health and Human Services must establish a mechanism to provide discounts to patients to ensure that they do not pay the fee."
